name: Mosaic #1
description: The genesis piece in the Will Shipley Mega Highlight Reel Collection is comprised of 220 high resolution pictures by Bart Boatwright ([@bartboat](https://twitter.com/bartboat)). Thank you to our friends at Dear Old Clemson ([@ClemsonNIL](https://twitter.com/ClemsonNIL)) for helping us create this commemorative piece that is free to all fans that sign up for the Will Shipley FanClub before Kickoff on Saturday October 1st.
